chapterFind: js:var json = getResCode();var codeJson = {};eval('codeJson=' + json);var res = {};var header = {};header.type = 1;header.title = codeJson.result.evaluate;header.url = codeJson.result.cover;res.data = [];res.data.push(header);for(var i = 0; i < codeJson.result.episodes.length; i++){var mo = codeJson.result.episodes[i];var r = {};r.type = 2;r.title = mo.index + mo.index_title;r.url = 'https://xukunx.cn/cx/bili/?cid=' + mo.cid +'&bid=1';res.data.push(r);}setChapterResult(res);
searchFind: js:var json = getResCode();var fires = {};var resJson = {};eval('resJson=' + json);var res = [];if(resJson.data.total <= 0){fires.data = [];setSearchResult(fires);}else {for(var i = 0; i<resJson.data.items.length;i++){var mo = resJson.data.items[i];var r = {};r.title =  mo.title;r.url = 'https://xukunx.cn/cx/bangumi/port.php?sid='+mo.season_id;res.push(r);} fires.data = res;setSearchResult(fires);}
